	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You need 4M x 4 bit 60ns asynchronous DRAMs which can be found on 72 pin SIMMs.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
